        "content": "<p>Since <code>lt</code> below always has a type mismatch, wouldn't we expect <code>nomatch lt</code> to typecheck?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pos</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pos</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">succ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pos</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pos</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">toNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">succ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">succ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">toNat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span clas